      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S finished in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and presents beautifully. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, consistent with careful road use. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior remains supple and free of any tears or unpleasant odors; the cabin has been a strictly smoke-free environment. While there is very light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, the rear seats look nearly untouched. All electronics, including the Bose Surround Sound system and the PCM navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a complete service log from Porsche-authorized centers. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, brake fluid flush, and a new set of high-performance tires. The twin-turbo V6 delivers smooth, robust power, and the PDK transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. This Macan S offers a premium driving experience for someone who appreciates a well-documented and honest vehicle.",
